      "text": "**Root Cause:** The `changesets` table creation migration (`002_changesets.sql`) was present and marked as applied in the `schema_migrations` table, but the table itself was missing from the database. This indicated that the migration had been recorded as applied but the SQL execution failed silently.\n\n**Fix Applied:**\n\n1. **Verified Migration SQL:** Confirmed that `migrations/002_changesets.sql` contains correct table creation statements\n\n1.\n1.\n\n**Changes Made:**\n\n- Applied missing database migration for changesets table\n- Verified table schema matches migration specifications\n- Tested end-to-end plan approval → changeset creation workflow\n\n**Verification:**",
